a woman on the couch

224
00:12:50,728 --> 00:12:52,979
who thinks she's in love with you,

225
00:12:53,259 --> 00:12:54,959
how you get off on that.

226
00:12:55,649 --> 00:12:56,733
Get off on it?

227
00:12:57,287 --> 00:12:59,237
I've seen how you look at me.

228
00:13:00,771 --> 00:13:02,071
You hold up that

229
00:13:02,473 --> 00:13:05,551
neutral face pretty well,
but I see when it slips

230
00:13:07,245 --> 00:13:09,246
and you're looking at my neck

231
00:13:11,367 --> 00:13:12,636
or my legs

232
