wondering what it would be like.

233
00:13:20,356 --> 00:13:22,509
Come on, paul,
you said you'd be honest.

234
00:13:23,899 --> 00:13:25,749
How about you drop the act?

235
00:13:26,185 --> 00:13:28,306
You know you'd rather have
me as a patient ten some

236
